full-mouthed
Homonym Number:
Word Class: adjective
Sense Number:  1
Definition:[used elsewhere but earliest in NZ] [of sheep] of four to five years of age.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
